	</div>
	<h1 class="post-headline" data-remote="post:2174:title">
		Trump Administration Tells Some Business Owners “Do Not Apply” for Coronavirus Loans
	</h1>
	<h4 class="post-deck" data-remote="post:2174:deck">
		SBA says people with criminal records aren&#39;t eligible for some emergency loans, even though experts say the law doesn&#39;t exclude them.
	</h4>
</div>


  <article class="post-2174">

    <aside class="col4">
      <div class="inner">

        <div class="post-byline">
            By <span><a href="http://www.themarshallproject.org/staff/eli-hager">Eli Hager</a></span>

        </div>
          <div class="post-byline-shim"></div>

        
